/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d44ac73e232624b42c12684b12492a8c72867af","tid":611993,"uid":71176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8c5103a46048fe9e0fcafca280b675a5c30f0177","tid":611993,"uid":24472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"巴打小心，我之前個朋友又係咁，隔咗一兩個星期就過咗身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:24:11.000Z","msg":"下 真係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲好後生又未嫁人唔想死住"},{"pid":"00352a04dd261570842430e333f193f5f7ed3f97","tid":611993,"uid":94774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T14:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打小心，我之前個朋友又係咁，隔咗一兩個星期就過咗身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>下 真係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我仲好後生又未嫁人唔想死住</blockquote><br />\n巴打小心，我之前個朋友係醫院飲左啖水，隔咗一兩個星期就過咗身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a20cde4a8ac2d7ebaf44860855fb5e16d966f2","tid":611993,"uid":82255,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T16:44:42.000Z","msg":"我都會咁<br />\n好大機會係骨發炎<br />\n我係胸骨對下面有時會無啦啦好痛.一停止動作就無事<br />\n初初以為心臟有事.之後發現係骨發炎"},{"pid":"0c685c7fd4213d1c992ef373e192f2f5e2f8afba","tid":611993,"uid":147386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T17:28:15.000Z","msg":"我都會<br />\n有時呼吸就無啦啦痛<br />\n但睇醫生又check唔到咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51c36e249f1fa89a8c449aa2ebf849838132bc22","tid":611993,"uid":89509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:59:27.000Z","msg":"可能係坐姿唔好引起嘅肋骨發炎<br />\n改正自己嘅坐姿一兩個星期之後就會冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過如果真係好痛我建議你睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d9f1f4a91b4a28ee5434577cc0427b14bdc930d","tid":611993,"uid":147586,"like":1,